        * autoconf/aclocal.m4 (CL_CANONICAL_HOST): Always define
          ac_config_guess and ac_config_sub. Then ignore requests for
          AC_CONFIG_AUX_DIR_DEFAULT or AC_CANONICAL_HOST.

